Package: SegColR
Title: Segment and Color Analysis Using Grounded SAM
Version: 0.1.0
Author: James Boyko [aut, cre]
Maintainer: James Boyko <jboyko@umich.edu>
Description: This package provides tools for image segmentation and color 
    analysis using Grounded SAM (Segment Anything Model). It interfaces with 
    Python libraries to perform advanced image processing tasks and offers 
    R functions for easy integration in R workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
